on run
	display dialog "Manual Setup Required" & return & return & "Please follow these steps:" & return & return & "1. Open Automator" & return & "2. Choose Service" & return & "3. Set: no input, any application" & return & "4. Add Run AppleScript action" & return & "5. Paste the provided code" & return & "6. Save as Illustrator Dual PDF Save" buttons {"OK"}
end run